The paper deals with the detection and localization of image manipulations using deep learning and resampling features. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) as well as multimedia (cs.MM) since it deals with digital images. The paper also deals with image forensics and security, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
